headline: Will Truist's (TFC) New Business Credit Card Redefine Its Digital Banking Ambitions?
summary: Earlier this month, Truist Financial Corporation introduced the Truist Business Premium Visa Infinite card, a premium credit card tailored for small businesses with substantial annual spending and offering cash-back incentives, loyalty bonuses, and high credit lines. This launch marks Truist as the first super-regional bank to offer a Visa Business Infinite product, highlighting its focus on innovative solutions for business owners in high-growth economic regions.
